data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  **WELCOME HOME** This beautiful 2021 built ENERGY EFFICIENT HOME feels like new and delivers a bright open concept, four bedrooms for versatile space in a great community just minutes from the Winter Haven Historic District! Solar panels help keep energy costs low, there are TILE FLOORS throughout the main living areas and the many windows let the natural light pour in. The home chef will appreciate the well equipped kitchen offering plenty of cabinet and counter space, large pantry for ample storage and an island with breakfast bar seating perfect for entertaining friends and family! Ideal SPLIT BEDROOMS deliver a spacious PRIMARY SUITE with a WALK-IN CLOSET and private en-suite bath boasting a DUAL SINK VANITY and large walk-in shower. Three additional bedrooms and two more full baths give you flexible options and room to grow! Your backyard is the perfect blank canvas to add on to the patio, bring your BBQ or start a garden, there are so many possibilities! In a great location with easy access to local shopping, dining, parks and the charm of the Historic District, McKenna Dr is an easy YES! Don’t wait to build  call today and schedule your private tour and start making memories for years to come!
